        <num>CCP 72</num>
        <heading>72.  Certain actions involving property</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 72.  Certain actions involving property
An action in which a sequestration is sought, or an action to enforce a mortgage or privilege by an ordinary proceeding, may be brought in the parish where the property, or any portion thereof, is situated.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=112229</p>
